Detailed Description

cvmx_pci_win_rd_addr

PCI_WIN_RD_ADDR = PCI Window Read Address Register

Writing the least-significant-byte of this register will cause a read operation to take place, UNLESS, a read operation is already taking place. A read is consider to end when the PCI_WIN_RD_DATA register is read.
